bject"></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase">EU Action to Tackle Youth Unemployment</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; text-transform:uppercase">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">Evidence Session No.</span><a name="bkEvNo"></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">2</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">              </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">              </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">Heard in </span><a name="bkEvidenceHeardInStatus"></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">Public</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">              </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">              </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none"> Questions</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-transform:n